<plot>Craig Ferguson hosts this 6 part TV series, focusing on historical sites throughout Scotland. He interviews Archeologists, Language experts, Scientists, Museum Curators and more, to "dig deep" into the past. Each episode focuses on a specific area or group of people, from the Cluniac Monks, the Picts and the Roman settlers, to the Isle of the Dead and the abandoned town of South Cobbinshaw.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?553514</url></doc>
